code: @Test public void invoke() {     new ApplicationContextRunner().withUserConfiguration(Config.class).run((context) -> {         ContextConditionEvaluation report = context.getBean(ConditionsReportEndpoint.class).applicationConditionEvaluation().getContexts().get(context.getId()).         assertThat(report.getPositiveMatches()).isEmpty().         assertThat(report.getNegativeMatches()).containsKey("a").         assertThat(report.getUnconditionalClasses()).contains("b").         assertThat(report.getExclusions()).contains("com.foo.Bar").     }). }

@PostConstruct public void setupAutoConfigurationReport() {     ConditionEvaluationReport report = ConditionEvaluationReport.get(this.context.getBeanFactory()).     report.recordEvaluationCandidates(Arrays.asList("a", "b")).     report.recordConditionEvaluation("a", mock(Condition.class), mock(ConditionOutcome.class)).     report.recordExclusions(Collections.singletonList("com.foo.Bar")). }
@Bean public ConditionsReportEndpoint endpoint() {     return new ConditionsReportEndpoint(this.context). }
